Cell["\<\
Dsolve returns a list of rules so we need to get the RHS.
Then we take limits.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.977230322894691*^9, 3.9772303437507143`*^9}, {
  3.977230951905744*^9, 
  3.977230959377356*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8f5f7a4a-a778-4f52-b011-\
